sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User
    participant F as Vue Frontend<br/>(Components)
    participant N as Nginx<br/>(Security Headers)
    participant R as Rate Limiter<br/>(slowapi)
    participant B as FastAPI Backend<br/>(structlog)
    participant P as PostgreSQL<br/>(Alembic)
    participant M as MinIO
    participant A as AI Provider or Fallback

    U->>F: Register or login
    F->>N: Auth request
    N->>R: Forward (5/min limit)
    R->>B: Validated request
    B->>P: Read or write user
    B-->>F: JWT token

    U->>F: Upload PDF
    F->>N: Multipart upload + JWT
    N->>B: Forward
    B->>M: Store file bytes
    B->>P: Store document metadata
    B-->>F: Document metadata

    U->>F: List documents (paginated)
    F->>N: GET /documents?skip=0&limit=20
    N->>B: Forward
    B->>P: Query with offset/limit + count
    B-->>F: {items, total, skip, limit}

    U->>F: Trigger async summary
    F->>N: Create summary job
    N->>R: Forward (10/min limit)
    R->>B: Validated request
    B->>P: Store processing job
    B-->>F: Job queued (202)
    B->>M: Download PDF
    B->>A: Generate summary from extracted text
    B->>P: Update document summary and job status
    F->>B: Poll job status
    B-->>F: Completed job and updated document state

    U->>F: Ask question over document
    F->>N: Question request + JWT
    N->>R: Forward (10/min limit)
    R->>B: Validated request (3-500 chars)
    B->>M: Download PDF
    B->>A: Generate answer
    B->>P: Store Q&A record
    B-->>F: Answer payload
